{"tid":2115302,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜再破尺度！造型藏驚人亮點　一撥髮「胸口炸裂」引暴動","createTime":"2020-07-19T11:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T13:28:52.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca2c27d58bdd6e5463d9177a10aa7ab9a1ef4b4","tid":2115302,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:49:26.000Z","msg":"[img]南韓女團TWICE中的台灣成員周子瑜，靠著甜美仙氣的外表，去年還獲選美國電影網站TC Candler公布「2019全球女星最美臉蛋」排行榜奪得冠軍。近日TWICE釋出預告形象照，成員們皆以白色西裝造型現身，子瑜的造型則藏有驚人亮點，引發粉絲熱議。[/img]<br />\n<br />\nTWICE將於9/16發行第三張日文精選專輯《#TWICE3》，近日釋出的預告形象照中，團員們化身上班女郎以白西裝造型帥氣現身，子瑜身穿白色長袖襯衫搭配白色長褲，乍看之下全身包緊緊，但她一撥髮時「胸肩處挖空」讓性感鎖骨全現形，粉絲暴動紛紛湧入留言「設計師好棒棒」、「我瑜威武」、「子瑜真的好美」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/17/2668920-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F17%2F2668920-XXL.jpg&h=e2ba814e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲TWICE釋出預告形象照，子瑜造型藏有性感亮點。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/17/2668922-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F17%2F2668922-XXL.jpg&h=0e811fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE本月初發表全新單曲《MORE &amp; MORE》，子瑜以一件綠色中空超激短裙驚艷全場，但其實早在四年前周子瑜的小蠻腰造型早就被粉絲廣為流傳，當時的她化身「啦啦隊女孩」穿上超短版削肩上衣，配上超亮眼的橘色百褶裙，頂著大太陽一邊跳舞一邊微笑面對鏡頭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/20/2619159-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F20%2F2619159-XXL.jpg&h=74124e88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲子瑜化身啦啦隊女孩。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/20/2619206-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F20%2F2619206-XXL.jpg&h=67c84731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE成員周子瑜一直都是門面擔當，去年還獲選美國電影網站TC Candler公布「2019全球女星最美臉蛋」排行榜奪得冠軍，同樣都是中空裝打扮，四年過去，周子瑜從可愛甜美蛻變成成熟女人味，不僅在專輯新造型裡面以中空裝現身，還小露事業線，纖細的小蠻腰、白皙長腿更是一覽無遺，身材好到讓粉絲不禁直呼「子瑜好辣」、「裙子太短了吧」，「好美喔！」粉絲看了鼻血狂流。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/25/2572839-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F25%2F2572839-XXL.jpg&h=f93113a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜獲選「2019全球女星最美臉蛋」排行榜冠軍。（圖／翻攝自臉書）"},{"pid":"99533245319ce24d95338b2e50cc134c285703e4","tid":2115302,"uid":108756,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"放相就唔該放重點相<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一野碌落去都唔知睇到乜"},{"pid":"86efded7c80e1d99b36394f2744b4e5db946fa33","tid":2115302,"uid":555,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"99533245319ce24d95338b2e50cc134c285703e4","tid":2115302,"uid":108756,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"放相就唔該放重點相<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一野碌落去都唔知睇到乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:58:00.000Z","msg":"樓主弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdf742f818e34e0a08fc8b65b1172751a591da2","tid":2115302,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"86efded7c80e1d99b36394f2744b4e5db946fa33","tid":2115302,"uid":555,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"99533245319ce24d95338b2e50cc134c285703e4","tid":2115302,"uid":108756,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"放相就唔該放重點相<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一野碌落去都唔知睇到乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:58:00.000Z","msg":"樓主弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:08:10.000Z","msg":"我SHARE報導姐"},{"pid":"40c6eea6c2a5af5370137e3eac94ce9916d5e7c6","tid":2115302,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:09:20.000Z","msg":"彩瑛又剪咗個柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0addc2743